<div><p>Se testeaza adaugarea unui produs</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc28737"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P236-17: TestCaseECP1_Valid_AdaugareProdus&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">maria_salejan05</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se creaza un produs avand toate atributele&nbsp;valide.&nbsp;</p>

<p>pret&gt;0</p>

<p>0&lt;length(nume)&lt;256</p>

