</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>nume is string</p>

<p>pret is double, pret&gt;0</p>

<p>0&lt;length(nume)&lt;256</p>

<p>id, tip si categorie sunt valide</p>
