<p>&nbsp;prod(</p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;id102;</p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;nume: &quot;preparat rece&quot;;</p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;pret: 13;</p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;categorie: JUICE;</p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;tip: WATER_BASED</p>

<p>&nbsp;)</p>

<p>se apeleaza addProduct(prod)</p>
</td><td><p>Produsul este adaugat in lista de produse</p>
